CE --> Container Engine like Docker
COE --> Container Orchestration Engine --> K8s
  Auto-scaling of containers (Horizontal Pod AutoScaler + Cluster AutoScaler)
  Auto-healing (self-healing)
  auto load-balancing of requests across containers
  auto-deployment to avoid downtime during deployment (rolling update, B/G deployment)
  
Open Cloudshell

Make sure, below 3 CLIs are installed:

aws cli --> aws --version
kubectl --> kubectl version
Install eksctl --> https://eksctl.io/installation/


eksctl create cluster eksdemo1

kubectl get pods

kubectl apply -f nginx-pod.yaml

kubectl delete -f nginx-pod.yaml

eksctl delete cluster eksdemo1
